author: Matt London
title: Country duo 'Big & Rich' to perform their coronavirus PSA 'Stay Home' live
description: The country music duo of Big Kenny and John Rich, known as "Big & Rich," created their own public service announcement as the country battles the coronavirus pandemic — and they'll be delivering it in the form of a song.
